name: Fender Aerodyne Jazz Electric Bass
features: The Aerodyne Jazz Bass offers timeless Fender tone, smooth playability, and alluring black-on-black style. A fresh take on a classic design, this J Bass packs plenty of sonic versatility by way of its dual pickup configuration. Built with a bound basswood body with a unique carved top, this bass unites classic Fender design with a striking set of updated features.

name: Dixon Drums Jet Set Plus
features: The Dixon Drums Jet Set Plus 5pc Shell Pack offers genuine versatility and practical solutions to all the logistical issues that drummers face. A true, all-in-one drum set, the Jet Set Plus can be used as either a compact acoustic kit, a silent practice kit or even a stand-up cocktail kit for busking and similar outdoor performances. For silent use, just flip the drums upside down to play on the silent mesh heads attached to their resonant sides. A separate silencing pad for the snare drum is included. Whether silent or full volume, the Jet Set Plus' 9-ply, mahogany shells produce rich warmth and resonance in all settings. From travelling to teaching, with smaller, more compact shell depths, the Jet Set Plus is an inspired choice for drummers on the move. Embrace the lifestyle of a working musician and prepare yourself for anything. Be Jet Set.

inBox.itemName: Silencing Pads for Cymbal and Snare

name: DP-6 Digital Piano
features: The DP-6 digital piano is the perfect piano for anyone who wishes to enhance their skills. With 88 full sized, hammer action keys you get the experience of an acoustic piano's resistance with all the benefits a digital piano can offer. Going digital allows you to perform alongside a fellow musician or your teacher using Duet mode, or push your sound into new territories thanks to Split or Dual mode.

name: Yamaha DTX6K-X Electronic Drum Kit
features: The heart of any electronic drum kit is the sound module. The DTX-PRO module features 712 different sounds, with 40-pre set kits ready to play. Using the catalogue of sounds provided, you can create up to 200 user kits, allowing you to instantly re-call for custom set-up. The sounds on the DTX-PRO are recorded in professional studios in high resolution, with careful consideration to the attack and release of each drum and cymbal to achieve a natural and realistic experience.

name: Roland VAD307 V-Drums Acoustic Design Drum Kit
features: The Roland VAD-307 V-Drums Acoustic Design Drum Kit is a lightweight electric drumkit created by Roland as part of their V-drum series. The main feature of this kit is the close resemblance to an acoustic drumkit. With deep rack toms, snare, and bass drum, this kit certainly looks and sounds like an acoustic kit. Constructed from wooden shells and featuring rubber cymbals, the Roland VAD-307 is designed to provide a realistic playing experience. The VAD-307 features a space-saving, lightweight frame - perfect for players with limited space to set their kit up. Complete with an array of 70 pre-set kits, built-in practice functions, and a hands-on interface allowing you to quickly and efficiently control your sound. A perfect choice for any drummer looking for a reliable electric drumkit, the Roland VAD-307 V-Drums Acoustic Design Drum Kit is a superb choice.

name: Yamaha DTX8K-X Electronic Drum Kit, Real Wood
features: The new definition of upper mid-range in Yamaha E-Drums has arrived. The new Yamaha DTX8K-X RW comes with an absorbing host of new features unique to the range. Yamaha have combined their knowledge of acoustic drums and integrated it into their E-Drum range, producing the newest in digital drumming, sampling, and music technology. Designed for players of all levels, the professional sounds and features offer a massive technological leap forward. Create, Inspire, Connect: this mantra stays true with the new DTX8 line.

name: DP-6 Digital Piano Pack, White
features: The DP-6 digital piano is the perfect piano for anyone who wishes to enhance their skills. With 88 full sized, hammer action keys you get the experience of an acoustic piano's resistance with all the benefits a digital piano can offer. Going digital allows you to perform alongside a fellow musician or your teacher using Duet mode, or push your sound into new territories thanks to Split or Dual mode.

name: DP-12 Compact Digital Piano, Matte Black
features: Enjoy the sound and feel of the real thing with 88 hammer-action keys. This advanced design will take your playing to new heights, especially with the unparalleled realism of 128-note polyphony. Take this further by embracing the three-pedal unit. As you use the soft, sostenuto, and sustain pedals you'll employ advanced piano techniques to ensure total expression.

name: Casio PX S6000 Digital Piano Stand Package, Black
features: Casio's latest Privias have been designed under the "In Harmony with Life" concept - for people who value design alongside modern technology and instrument quality. With an interior-friendly blended body, the PX-S6000 is just as suited to your living room to a performance space. This piano has a glossy black design with walnut wood grain and high quality speaker fabric, yet is still portable coming in at an extremely lightweight 14.8 kg. Perfect as a fully functional statement piece, there is a separate stand available.

name: Dreadnought Acoustic Guitar, Black
features: The Dreadnought Acoustic Guitar by Gear4music offers the perfect start for those taking their first steps into the world of the guitar. Constructed using the same techniques as our top of the range acoustics, the Dreadnought will grow with you as you progress. Thanks to its all-hardwood construction, the Dreadnought offers an exceptional tone and a quality build that is designed to withstand the rigours of continued play and practice. Its spruce top finish offers the right amount of brightness, allowing you to cut through the densest of arrangements, whilst the basswood body ensures a warm, balanced tone. When merged, they offer a great all-rounder, suitable for a broad range of musical styles.

name: 3/4 LA Bass Guitar + 15W Amp Pack, Black
features: The 3/4 LA Bass Guitar & Amp Pack combines the classic looks and tone of our small scale bass guitar with a 15W bass amp - a set ideal for younger players, or anyone who just prefers a smaller and lighter bass guitar. Our miniature amp is an affordable and convenient rehearsal and practice solution for either, and comes with a lead and strap; making this a great starter pack at unrivalled value.

name: Hartwood Villanelle Cutaway Electro Acoustic Guitar, Satin Black
features: The Hartwood Villanelle Cutaway Acoustic Guitar is an instrument suitable for a range of styles and techniques. Ideal for big powerful open chords, the solid spruce top opens up to create a large sound, that also responds well to delicate finger picking. An ergonomic cutaway design also offers easy access to the higher frets, making the guitar suitable for a range of pieces. The Hartwood Villanelle is a great guitar for stage and studio!
